{"tid":963651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港真係無救啦","createTime":"2018-12-31T16:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T18:01:59.000Z","uid":205231,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e4dc39d5a26d8791f4316249babae4645412ba31","tid":963651,"uid":205231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T16:19:10.000Z","msg":"話說今日小弟去倒數，去文化中心一齊戇鳩鳩食賓周，同朋友人逼人。當12點倒數，啲人用蝗語倒數10聲(我唔排除有台灣人)，我當堂呆咗。其實喺香港倒數，可以尊重吓本地文化？用廣東話倒數真係好難？如果本地人都要跟住一齊用蝗語倒數就真係無救。<br />\n<br />\n保護下一代，由你我做起。"},{"pid":"d41e5fc5de95b218c9df138c4e80cbe4b1ccfedd","tid":963651,"uid":3220,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T17:50:57.000Z","msg":"用英文點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b3b7560454f1f94fc9089fe4ce2c0c3b30b673","tid":963651,"uid":205231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d41e5fc5de95b218c9df138c4e80cbe4b1ccfedd","tid":963651,"uid":3220,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T17:50:57.000Z","msg":"用英文點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T18:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}